Yekker-iyi-d fell-as. 
Bɣiɣ-kem deg usu-w. 
Bɣiɣ-k deg usu-w. 
Tenɣiḍ-iyi s tqendurt-nni tesliḍ, a ssimra! 
Tesɛiḍ tibbucin sehbalent arrac. 
Tesɛiḍ iffan sehbalen arrac. 
Iwala-kem yekker-as-d. 
Twala-t dɣa tger afus-is ɣer ger iḍaṛen-is. 
Tḥemmel ad as-selfeɣ ger iḍaṛen-is. 
Ur ɛad serseɣ imi-w ɣef yimi-s dɣa teɣli-d ɣef yedmaren-iw.
Nemɛebbaṛ deg usu ḥala mi yuli wass. 
Cedhaɣ ad waliɣ lesrar-im. 
Ḥemleɣ ad waliɣ lesrar-im. 
Taɣma-m tessehbal arrac. 
Tafekka-k tessehbal tullas. 
Tekkes taqendurt-is, ḥareɣ ansi ara s-kkeɣ. 
Yekkes asarwal-is, xelɛeɣ mi walaɣ lesrar-is. 
Tikelt tamezwarut mi walaɣ lesrar-is tecfi-id tidi d tasemmaḍ. 
Ḥemleɣ ad sudneɣ tizizaḥin-im. 
Ḥemleɣ ad sudneɣ tibbucin-im. 
Tusa-tt-id ccehwa n tayri dɣa tɛerḍ-iyi ɣer texxamt-is. 
Tusa-id ccehwa n tayri, dɣa ɛerḍeɣ-tt-id ɣer texxamt-iw. 
Tikelt tamezwarut deg gneɣ akked tmeṭṭut, wwiɣ-d tafat s wudem. 
Terɣa fell-as.
Yerɣa fell-as.
Terɣa fell-ak.
Yerɣa fell-am.
Ah! A limmer ad gneɣ yid-m ukan ssaɛa!
Ah! A limmer ad gneɣ yid-k ukan ssaɛa!
Mi kem-walaɣ ad iyi-d-yekker.
Mi k-walaɣ ad iyi-d-tas ccehwa fell-ak.
Ay akka qurent tebbucin-im.
Ay akka leqqaqit tebbucin-im.
Bɣiɣ ad waiɣ laɛmeṛ-im deg usu.
Bɣiɣ ad waiɣ laɛmeṛ-ik deg usu.
Ḥemleɣ ad kem-waliɣ ɛeryan.
Ḥemleɣ ad k-waliɣ ɛeryan.
Caṛweɣ mi d-teqqimeḍ fell-i.
Ḥusseɣ i wul-iw la ijeffel ass mi d-tkecmeḍ deg-i tikelt tamezwarut.
Ḥusseɣ i wul-iw la ijeffel ass mi kecmeḍ deg-m tikelt tamezwarut.













































